      "job_description": "Marketers on Demand is currently seeking a Web Developer for our innovative, fast-growing client! We are ideally looking for someone who will optimize their website's performance, ensure exceptional user experience and drive higher conversion rates.\n\nThis is a Hybrid role in Toronto, with 2 days a week in office.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n\n• Oversee the end-to-end development of their website (planning, testing, and launching new pages)\n• Create custom elements within WordPress using efficient, reusable, and reliable code\n• Work collaboratively to enhance site functionality, user experience, and conversion rates\n• Engage with external development teams on various projects\n• Implement improvements that increase website performance, optimize speed, usability, and search engine rankings\n\nKey Qualifications:\n\n• Over 2 years of experience with content management systems and WordPress\n• Experience building new webpages as well as through templates\n• A strong understanding of standard web development (craft clean, reusable code in HTML, CSS and JavaScript for web experiences in a mobile-first environment)\n• Experience with website analytics (GA4) and other web integration tools (ex. GTM and Optimizely)\n• A solid understanding of technical SEO best practices (work with a content team to implement on-page SEO elements)\n\nIf interested, please apply directly or reach out to mark.brosas@marketersondemand.com for more info!",
